  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Full time/Locum Dentists",
  "description": "<p>Passionate about dental care?</p><p><br /></p><p>With three conveniently located clinics in Ang Mo Kio, Bedok, and Orchard, <strong>WeSmile Dental Care</strong> is your trusted partner in oral health. We are dedicated to delivering dental excellence for your everyday care, with a mission to inspire confidence and create healthy smiles that enhance your quality of life.</p><p><br /></p><p>With a team of dedicated and experienced dentists, we offer a comprehensive range of preventative, restorative and aesthetic dental services — from scaling and polishing, dental implants, root canal treatments, teeth aligner, veneers and more.</p><p>If you are registered with the Singapore Dental Council and hold a valid practising certificate, we'd love to share more about our opportunities. Dental officers who are in the final year of bond are welcome to apply as well.</p><p><br /></p><p><u>Who we're looking for</u></p><ul><li>BDS or equivalent qualifications recognized by the Singapore Dental Council.</li><li>Determined, committed with gentle and caring nature</li><li>Excellent communication and good interpersonal skills</li><li>Friendly, respectful towards others and able to work well in a family-like team</li></ul><p>Please email us your resume to <a href=\"mailto:xinying@wesmiledental.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">amelia@wesmiledental.sg</a>.</p>",
